<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Laborat√≥rio - Admin</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #0f172a; --panel: #1e293b; --accent: #3498db; --text: #e2e8f0; --danger: #e74c3c; --success: #2ecc71; --warning: #f1c40f; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h1 { margin: 0; color: var(--warning); text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(241, 196, 15, 0.3); font-size: 1.8rem; }
        .back-btn { text-decoration: none; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 8px; transition: 0.2s; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        .back-btn:hover { background: #333; color: #fff; border-color: #555; }
        .main-layout { display: flex; gap: 20px; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
        .sidebar { width: 320px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
        .sidebar-header { padding: 15px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .list-container { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 10px; display: none; }
        .list-container.active { display: block; }
        .list-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .list-item:hover { background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); }
        .list-item img, .npc-thumb { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); image-rendering: pixelated; object-fit: contain; flex-shrink: 0; border: 1px solid #444; }
        .npc-thumb { background-size: 400% auto; background-position: 0 0; }
        .item-info { flex: 1; overflow: hidden; }
        .item-name { font-weight: bold; color: #fff; font-size: 1rem; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
        .item-sub { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #777; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
        .editor-area { flex: 1; background: var(--panel); border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; overflow-y: auto; border: 1px solid #333; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .tabs { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; }
        .tab-btn { background: none; border: none; padding: 10px 25px; color: #777; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -2px; transition: 0.2s; }
        .tab-btn:hover { color: #aaa; }
        .tab-btn.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }
        .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .full-width { grid-column: span 3; }
        .half-width { grid-column: span 2; }
        label { display: block; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        input, select, textarea { width: 100%; background: #0f172a; border: 1px solid #334155; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: 0.2s; }
        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus { border-color: var(--accent); outline: none; background: #162032; }
        input[disabled] { background: #1e293b; color: #555; border-color: #222; }
        .moves-wrapper { background: #0f172a; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; max-height: 220px; overflow-y: auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; }
        .move-option { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; border: 1px solid transparent; }
        .move-option:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: #444; }
        .move-option input[type="checkbox"] { width: auto; margin: 0; cursor: pointer; }
        .move-lvl-input { width: 45px; padding: 2px; font-size: 0.75rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #555; background: #000; color: var(--accent); border-radius: 4px; }
        .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #333; }
        button { cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        button:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
        .btn-save { flex: 1; padding: 14px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; background: var(--success); color: #052e16; font-size: 1rem; }
        .btn-save:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }
        .btn-delete { flex: 0.3; padding: 14px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; background: var(--danger); color: #fff; font-size: 1rem; }
        .btn-delete:hover { background: #c0392b; }
        .btn-new { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: none; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 5px; }
        .btn-new:hover { background: #2980b9; }
        .hidden { display: none; }
        h4 { color: var(--warning); border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 25px; font-size: 1rem; }
        #imgPreview, #npcImgPreview { margin-top:10px; height:80px; border:1px dashed #444; border-radius: 6px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); color: #555; overflow: hidden; }
        #imgPreview img, #npcImgPreview img { height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
        .code-area { font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; color: #2ecc71; background: #000; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.4; }
        .mini-btn { width: auto; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #334155; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; }
        .mini-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10); }
        .row-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
        .row-item { display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 90px 46px; gap:10px; align-items:center; }
        .row-item.shop { grid-template-columns: 1fr 110px 46px; }
        .row-remove { background: var(--danger); border: none; color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; height: 40px; }
        details.advanced { border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
        details.advanced summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 800; color: #94a3b8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div>
            <h1>LABORAT√ìRIO</h1>
            <small style="color:#777">Painel de Cria√ß√£o e Balanceamento</small>
        </div>
        <a href="/city?userId=<%= user._id %>" class="back-btn">‚¨ÖÔ∏è VOLTAR AO JOGO</a>
    </header>

    <div class="main-layout">
        <!-- SIDEBAR -->
        <div class="sidebar">
            <div id="list-poke" class="list-container active">
                <div class="sidebar-header">POKEMONS (<%= pokemons.length %>)</div>
                <div style="padding:10px;">
                    <button class="btn-new" onclick="clearPokeForm()"><span>+</span> NOVO POKEMON</button>
                </div>
                <% pokemons.forEach(p => { %>
                    <div class="list-item" onclick="loadPokemon(<%= JSON.stringify(p) %>)">
                        <img src="<%= (p.sprite && (p.sprite.startsWith('http') || p.sprite.startsWith('data:'))) ? p.sprite : '/uploads/' + p.sprite %>" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                        <div class="item-info">
                            <div class="item-name"><%= p.name %></div>
                            <div class="item-sub">Tipo: <%= p.type %> | Spawn: <%= p.spawnLocation || 'Nenhum' %></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
            <div id="list-npc" class="list-container">
                <div class="sidebar-header">NPCS (<%= npcs.length %>)</div>
                <div style="padding:10px;">
                    <button class="btn-new" onclick="clearNpcForm()"><span>+</span> NOVO NPC</button>
                </div>
                <% npcs.forEach(n => { %>
                    <div class="list-item" onclick="loadNpc(<%= JSON.stringify(n) %>)">
                        <% if(n.isCustomSkin) { %> 
                            <div class="npc-thumb" style="background-image: url('<%= n.skin %>')"></div>
                        <% } else { %> 
                            <div class="npc-thumb" style="background-image: url('/uploads/<%= n.skin || 'char1' %>.png')"></div> 
                        <% } %>
                        <div class="item-info">
                            <div class="item-name"><%= n.name %></div>
                            <div class="item-sub"><%= n.map %> (X:<%= n.x %>, Y:<%= n.y %>)</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- EDITOR AREA -->
        <div class="editor-area">
            <div class="tabs">
                <button id="btn-tab-poke" class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchMode('poke')">POKEMON</button>
                <button id="btn-tab-npc" class="tab-btn" onclick="switchMode('npc')">NPC</button>
            </div>

            <!-- ================= FORM POKEMON ================= -->
            <div id="tab-poke" class="tab-content">
                <form id="pokeForm" action="/lab/create" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" onsubmit="prepareMoves()">
                    <input type="hidden" name="existingId" id="existingId">
                    <input type="hidden" name="movesJson" id="movesJson">
                    
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div>
                            <label>ID (Gerado Auto)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="id" id="pokeId" disabled placeholder="Novo">
                        </div>
                        <div class="half-width">
                            <label>Nome do Monstro</label>
                            <input type="text" name="name" id="pokeName" required autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div>
                            <label>Tipo Elementar</label>
                            <select name="type" id="pokeType">
                                <% Object.keys(types).forEach(t => { %> <option value="<%= t %>"><%= t.toUpperCase() %></option> <% }) %>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div><label>Chance Captura (0.1 - 1.0)</label><input type="number" step="0.1" name="catchRate" id="pokeRate" value="0.5" min="0" max="1"></div>
                        <div><label>Raridade de Spawn (%)</label><input type="number" name="spawnChance" id="pokeSpawn" value="10"></div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h4>üìç SPAWN & EVOLU√á√ÉO</h4>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div>
                            <label>Local de Spawn (ID do Mapa)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="location" id="pokeLoc" placeholder="ex: city, house1" list="mapSuggestions">
                            <datalist id="mapSuggestions">
                                <option value="city">Cidade</option>
                                <option value="forest">Floresta</option>
                            </datalist>
                        </div>
                        <div><label>N√≠vel M√≠nimo</label><input type="number" name="minLvl" id="spawnMin" value="2"></div>
                        <div><label>N√≠vel M√°ximo</label><input type="number" name="maxLvl" id="spawnMax" value="5"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Evolu√ß√£o (ID do Alvo + N√≠vel)</label>
                            <div style="display:flex; gap:10px;">
                                <input type="text" name="evoTarget" id="evoTarget" placeholder="ex: charizard (ID)" autocomplete="off">
                                <input type="number" name="evoLevel" id="evoLevel" placeholder="Lv 16" style="width:120px;">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h4>üìä STATUS BASE</h4>
                    <div class="form-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);">
                        <div><label>HP</label><input type="number" name="hp" id="statHp" required value="40"></div>
                        <div><label>EN (Mana)</label><input type="number" name="energy" id="statEn" required value="100"></div>
                        <div><label>ATK</label><input type="number" name="atk" id="statAtk" required value="50"></div>
                        <div><label>DEF</label><input type="number" name="def" id="statDef" required value="40"></div>
                        <div><label>SPD</label><input type="number" name="spd" id="statSpd" required value="50"></div>
                    </div>

                    <h4>‚öîÔ∏è MOVEPOOL (Ataques)</h4>
                    <div class="moves-wrapper">
                        <% Object.keys(moves).forEach(moveKey => { const m = moves[moveKey]; %>
                            <div class="move-option" title="Poder: <%= m.power %> | Tipo: <%= m.element %>">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="move-check" data-id="<%= moveKey %>" id="chk_<%= moveKey %>">
                                <span style="flex:1"><%= m.name %></span>
                                <input type="number" class="move-lvl-input" id="lvl_<%= moveKey %>" value="1" title="N√≠vel para aprender">
                            </div>
                        <% }) %>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid" style="margin-top:20px;">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Sprite (PNG/GIF)</label>
                            <input type="file" name="sprite" accept="image/*" onchange="previewImage(this, 'imgPreview')">
                            <div id="imgPreview">Sem imagem</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; cursor:pointer; background:#162032; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #333; margin-top:10px;">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="isStarter" id="isStarter" style="width:auto;"> <span style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--accent);">Dispon√≠vel como Inicial?</span>
                    </label>
                    
                    <div class="btn-row">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-save">üíæ SALVAR POKEMON</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-delete" onclick="deleteItem('deleteForm')">üóëÔ∏è EXCLUIR</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                <form id="deleteForm" action="/lab/delete" method="POST" style="display:none;"><input type="hidden" name="id" id="deleteId"></form>
            </div>

            <!-- ================= FORM NPC ================= -->
            <div id="tab-npc" class="tab-content hidden">
                <form id="npcForm" action="/lab/create-npc" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <input type="hidden" name="userId" value="<%= user._id %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="npcId" id="npcId">
                    
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Nome do NPC</label>
                            <input type="text" name="name" id="npcName" required autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div>
                            <label>Mapa (ID)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="map" id="npcMap" list="mapList" placeholder="ex: city, house1" required autocomplete="off">
                            <datalist id="mapList">
                                <option value="lobby">Lobby</option>
                                <option value="forest">Floresta</option>
                                <option value="city">Cidade</option>
                            </datalist>
                        </div>
                        <div><label>Posi√ß√£o X (0-100%)</label><input type="number" name="x" id="npcX" value="50"></div>
                        <div><label>Posi√ß√£o Y (0-100%)</label><input type="number" name="y" id="npcY" value="50"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div>
                            <label>Dire√ß√£o Inicial</label>
                            <select name="direction" id="npcDir">
                                <option value="down">Baixo</option>
                                <option value="up">Cima</option>
                                <option value="left">Esquerda</option>
                                <option value="right">Direita</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Skin Padr√£o</label>
                            <select name="skinSelect" id="npcSkinSelect">
                                <option value="">-- Personalizada --</option>
                                <% for(let i=1; i<=12; i++){ %> <option value="char<%=i%>">Personagem <%=i%></option> <% } %>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Recompensa ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" name="money" id="npcMoney" value="100">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">
                        <label>Ou Upload Skin Pr√≥pria</label>
                        <input type="file" name="npcSkinFile" accept="image/*" onchange="previewImage(this, 'npcImgPreview')">
                        <div id="npcImgPreview"></div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- BACKGROUND DE BATALHA COM UPLOAD -->
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Cen√°rio de Batalha (Upload Imagem)</label>
                            <input type="file" name="battleBgFile" accept="image/*" onchange="previewImage(this, 'battleBgPreview')">
                            <div id="battleBgPreview" style="margin-top:5px; height:60px; border:1px dashed #555; display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; overflow:hidden;">
                                <span style="font-size:0.7rem; color:#555">Padr√£o</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h4>üí¨ DI√ÅLOGOS</h4>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Fala Inicial (Antes da Luta)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="dialogue" id="npcDialogue" placeholder="Ei voc√™! Vamos batalhar!" required autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="half-width">
                            <label>Fala de Vit√≥ria (Jogador venceu)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="winDialogue" id="npcWinDialogue" placeholder="Voc√™ √© forte..." autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Fala em Cooldown (J√° derrotado)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="cooldownDialogue" id="npcCdDialogue" placeholder="Volte mais tarde." autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h4 style="margin-top:20px;">üéí EQUIPE POKEMON</h4>
                    <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; margin-bottom:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                        <button type="button" class="mini-btn" onclick="npcTeamAddRow()">+ adicionar monstro</button>
                        <button type="button" class="mini-btn" onclick="npcTeamClear()">limpar</button>
                        <div style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#9aa7bd;">(gera o JSON automaticamente)</div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="npcTeamRows" class="row-list"></div>

                    <details class="advanced" style="margin-top:10px;">
                        <summary>Avan√ßado (JSON)</summary>
                        <textarea name="teamJson" id="npcTeam" class="code-area" style="height:100px;" placeholder='[{"baseId":"bulbasaur", "level":5}]'></textarea>
                    </details>

                    <select id="npcTeamPokemonOptionsTemplate" class="hidden">
                        <option value="">-- escolha um monstro --</option>
                        <% pokemons.forEach(p => { %>
                            <option value="<%= p.id %>"><%= p.name %> (<%= p.id %>)</option>
                        <% }) %>
                    </select>

                    <h4 style="margin-top:20px;">üéÅ ITEM DE RECOMPENSA (Opcional)</h4>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div><label>Cooldown (Minutos)</label><input type="number" name="cooldownMinutes" id="npcCooldown" value="0" title="0 = √önico, >0 = Repet√≠vel"></div>
                        <div><label>ID do Item/Pokemon</label><input type="text" name="rewardVal" id="npcRewVal" placeholder="ex: pokeball, rareCandy" autocomplete="off"></div>
                        <div><label>Quantidade</label><input type="number" name="rewardQty" id="npcRewQty" value="1"></div>
                        <input type="hidden" name="rewardType" id="npcRewType" value="item">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
                        <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; cursor:pointer; background:#162032; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #333;">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="rewardKeyItem" id="npcRewardKeyItem" style="width:auto;"> <span style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--accent);">Recompensa √© item-chave?</span>
                        </label>
                        <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; cursor:pointer; background:#162032; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #333;">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="rewardUnique" id="npcRewardUnique" style="width:auto;"> <span style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--accent);">Recompensa √∫nica?</span>
                        </label>
                        <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; cursor:pointer; background:#162032; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #333;">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="blocksMovement" id="npcBlocksMovement" style="width:auto;"> <span style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--accent);">NPC bloqueia caminho?</span>
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <h4 style="margin-top:20px;">üß© INTERA√á√ÉO (Quest / Itens)</h4>
                    <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; cursor:pointer; background:#162032; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #333;">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="interactEnabled" id="npcInteractEnabled" style="width:auto;"> <span style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--warning);">Habilitar intera√ß√£o (al√©m/sem batalha)</span>
                    </label>

                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Servi√ßo do NPC (opcional)</label>
                            <select name="interactServiceType" id="npcInteractServiceType">
                                <option value="">Quest / Itens (padr√£o)</option>
                                <option value="heal">Curar time</option>
                                <option value="shop">Loja</option>
                            </select>
                            <div class="hint" style="margin-top:6px; color:#9aa7bd; font-size:0.85rem;">Para "Curar time" e "Loja", a intera√ß√£o N√ÉO √© √∫nica por padr√£o.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Texto de cura (se servi√ßo = Curar time)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="interactHealDialogue" id="npcInteractHealDialogue" placeholder="Posso curar seus monstros!" autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="full-width">
                            <label>Itens da loja (JSON) (se servi√ßo = Loja)</label>
                            <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; margin-bottom:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
